results.occurrenceRemarks: A record shot of the first two Wattled Cranes that we saw in Bwabwata N.P. We ended up seeing five of them there, which was cool because they are a pretty rare species, listed as Vulnerable. This photo isn't very good, but you can just barely see the two wattles that hang down on each side of the bill, and the red facial patch.
